            { title: 'Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)', description: 'Enterprise data engineers convert a company\'s 10,000 internal documents into mathematical vectors using the "Embeddings" API; they then use the GPT-4 API to allow employees to query the database, ensuring the AI only answers using the company\'s private data.' },
            { title: 'Automated Audio Transcription', description: 'A podcasting platform integrates the "Whisper" API into its backend; whenever a creator uploads a raw MP3, the API autonomously transcribes the entire 2-hour file with near-human accuracy in seconds.' },
            { title: 'Autonomous AI Agents', description: 'Advanced developers utilize the "Assistants API" (Function Calling) to build autonomous agents that do not just chat, but can execute code, browse the live web, and trigger external APIs (like sending an email or booking a flight) based on natural language logic.' }
