        pricing_overview: `<p>Pictory operates on a tiered SaaS subscription model (Standard, Premium, Teams). The tiers are heavily gated by the monthly allowance of video rendering time, the length of videos allowed, the number of AI voiceover assets utilized, and access to premium music and stock footage libraries. A short free trial is typically available.</p>`,
        comparison_summary: `<p>Pictory competes directly against InVideo, Lumen5, and Descript. Descript is the undisputed king of highly precise, professional podcast editing and high-end transcript manipulation. Lumen5 is an older, slightly more corporate text-to-video player. InVideo is highly similar but leans slightly more toward complex manual template manipulation. Pictory differentiates itself as the absolute master of *Rapid Content Repurposing*. If the objective is to take a massive text asset and aggressively chop it into 10 high-quality, B-roll heavy, captioned social media clips with absolute minimum human interaction, Pictory is the superior automation engine.</p>`
